quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,Wa…óanaa lam …óemngal goongungal ka sakkitii…ìe …ìen
  26,85,Wa…óaa mi jeyaa…óo e ronoo…ìe Aljanna Neemaaji …óin
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaa…óo e majju…ìe …ìen"
  26,87,Wata A hersinoyam √ëalnde …ìe Immital
  26,88,√ëalnde nde jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe nafataa
  26,89,Si wanaa on ardu…óo ka Alla e …ìernde hisunde
  26,90,Aljanna on …ìatinanee huloo…ìe Alla …ìen
  26,91,Jahiim ngen fe√±√±inanee bew…ìe …ìen
  26,92,"∆Åe wi'nee: \"Honto woni ko laatino…óon kon hi…óon rewa"
  26,93,Gaanin Alla? Taw si …ói wallay on maa…óum …ói wallay hoore majji
  26,94,∆Åe hippee e nder magge kan…ìe e bew…ìe …ìen
  26,95,E konnuuji ibliisa …óin …ói fow majji
  26,96,∆Åe wi'i tawi kam…ìe hi…ìe wennjondira nder ton
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla, men woniino e nder majjere …ìanngunde"
  26,98,Tuma nde men fonnunoo on e Jooma winndere nden
  26,99,Majjinaali men si wonaa bon…ìe …ìen
  26,100,Alanaa men tefoo…ìe
  26,101,Wanaa kadi gi…óo √±allam…ìereejo(tigi tigi)
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men rutteede, men laatoo jeyaa…ìe e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,105,Yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen fenni Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,108,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,110,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,111,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gom…óinte, jaasu…ìe …ìen no jokkumaa"
